.dommeq.com/images/Photos/v.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: EQ monthly costs raise to 12.95 a month..</span><hr size=1> Prices go up over time folks, it is called inflation.  In addition to inflation here they have added a lot more infrastructure that needs to be supported.  Actually just checking on a few other boards the majority of people seem indifferent to the change. (It is early though).  I think most people will take the change in stride and not think much of it.  <br><br>Some people may leave, but I don't think the effect over all will be noticeable.  It is hard to raise prices, some people will always complain, but life goes on.  <br><br>People who enjoy playing the game will continue, we can only hope that the extreme whiners will take this as the last straw (although the last straw never seems to break them) and leave the rest of us in piece. <p><p style="margin-top: -2; margin-bottom: 1"> </p><p style="margin-top: -2; margin-bottom: 1"><b><font color="#808000">               </font></b></p><table border="0" width="49%" bgcolor="#000080">  <tr>    <td width="57%"><b><font color="#808000" face="Arial">VowelumosConsonantario</font></b></td>    <td width="43%"><font color="#808000" face="Arial"><b>55 Preserver </b></font></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="57%"><font color="#FF0000" face="Arial"><b>Whoume Wearami </b></font></td>    <td width="43%"><font color="#FF0000" face="Arial"><b>26 Rogue</b></font></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="100%" colspan="2">      <p align="center"><font color="#FFFFFF"><b><i>Dragonsof Mesa Moon</i> on<i> </i> Tholuxe Paels</b> </font></td>  </tr></table><p style="margin-top: -2; margin-bottom: 1"> </p><p style="margin-top: -2; margin-bottom: 1"> </p><p style="margin-top: -2; margin-bottom: 1"> </p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/